    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142630/extras/aa1d91c2ff3d244ada506f82a1517745.avif?t=1732660887\" width=616 height=176 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>6</strong> Unique enemy types<br></li><li><strong>5</strong> Unique bosses<br></li><li>All color and shape coded</li></ul>The many enemies you'll face look and behave differently, but they have one thing in common. <u>They</u> want <i>you</i> <strong>dead</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142630/extras/ea42f89be5ecebca4974635344136cf9.avif?t=1732660887\" width=616 height=176 /></span><br><strong>22</strong> <i>unique </i>upgrades, helping you fight more effectivley. Beware, the higher your level, the more enemies come your way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142630/extras/0e69f86f101a6f1c74f7b554baef2e9c.avif?t=1732660887\" width=616 height=176 /></span><br>The <strong>3</strong> unique classes you can play as all have their unique strengths and weaknesses, each requiring a different playstyle as well as having their own upgrade pools.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Modifiers</h2>Is the game too easy or too hard? or do you want to just mix up the gameplay? There's currently <strong>5</strong> different modifiers to spice up the game.",
